---
title: Creamy Chickpea & Spinach Curry with Basmati Rice & Mint Yoghurt
description: When the days are cold and the nights are long it's curry's time to shine! This golden bowl of goodness has everything you need to feel cosy and satisfied, with chickpeas and veggies cooked in a creamy, mildly spiced sauce plus a cooling mint yoghurt to finish it off.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5cf77aebcf2d63001662689e-73e9ae4c.jpg
